page.title: 11TRAFFIC THROUGH BEAULIEU
page.content: We went to Beaulieu and did a traffic census. We were trying to find out what was the most popular car colour. We found out that red was the most popular because we saw 45 . Blue was the second with 41 and white was 3rd with 39. Altogether we saw {211 }cars in approximately half an hour. We saw a lot more cars from Dibden Purlieu than we did to Dibden Purlieu. Then we did a traffic census of how many people per car there were. We found 82 cars with 1 person in, 62 cars with 2 people and 6 with 3 people in. That was in half an hour.We saw a white Porsche and a black Rolls Royce. We saw {263}people in {211 }cars.
